          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A self-supporting beryllium metal foil of",
                "9.1 mg/cm2 thickness."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two 5.1 x 3.2 cm NaI crystals operated in",
                "fast-slow coincidence."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC",
                "GSPEC",
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The proton current 60 nA was",
                "collected in a Faraday cup. The beam was pulsed:",
                "0.7 sec irradiation interval, a 10.0 sec counting",
                "interval. The target was mounted at the center of an",
                "annular aluminum stopper 10 cm long, and with a wall",
                "thickness of 3.8 cm. Pairs of 511 keV quanta were",
                "detected in two NaI crystals operated in fast-slow",
                "coincidence. The coincidence resolving time of the",
                "detectors was 12 nsec full width at half maximum.",
                "The absolute efficiency of the apparatus as a detector",
                "of B-8 positrons was obtained in two stages: (i) The",
                "distribution of the stopped positrons in the aluminum",
                "stopper was calculated; and (ii) a Na-22 source of",
                "known strength was used to measure experimentally the",
                "efficiency."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Correction was made:",
                "- to take into account those B-8 nuclei which recoil",
                "  out of the target at angles such as to be lost; this",
                "  correction is approximately 4% at Ep = 30 MeV and",
                "  12% at Ep =47.5 MeV,",
                "- for positron annihilation in flight. '"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The errors on the cross sections were",
                "obtained by adding in quadrature statistical errors in",
                "the number of counts attributed to B-8, statistical",
                "errors in the background subtraction, inaccuracy in",
                "the estimation of time at which the beam was cut off."
              ]
            },
